Ended up here by accident.  We walked from the nearby Cashman center, so we wouldn't have to move the car.  The restaurant we were heading for was closed and we stopped here instead.  What a great surprise!  Really loved the food and it was very affordable.  Our table had tasty papusas and I ordered the churrasco.  Felt like a well appreciated neighborhood restaurant.
